Name: Female Prison
About the game: The player plays the role of a prison officer in a women's prison who is in charge of the inmates. · This is a prison themed role-playing and simulation business game. · The player assumes the role of a prison guard in charge of a prison. · The player needs certain strategies to keep the prison running properly and keep the indicators above a certain score. · Different prisoners have different levels of violence. · Grow assets as much as possible. · Increase order as much as possible. · If you've ever fantasized about being a prison guard and managing prisoners in your own way, don't miss this game!
